     C     *INZSR        BEGSR
 
     C     *ENTRY        PLIST
     C                   PARM                    ReturnCode
     C                   PARM                    SCOVE
     C                   PARM                    MsgIDXArr
     C                   PARM                    FldNamXArr
 
